column5: There is a open bass tournament out of Crystal beach on Sun oct. 18th, 2 man teams,$50 a team and that includs big fish, supposed to be sunny with 5 km winds should be a great day, 7:00 a.m start to 2:00 p.m, must have working livewells , no live bait, 5 fish limit, catch and release, again at the Crystal beach launch.
Sunday Is the 19th!!! So what day is it ??
It is the 19th my bad LOL!

Dang, wish this was posted sooner. I wrote this week's schedule, could have booked it off.  Good luck to all of those who head out! Smallie action is intense right now, should be some heavy weights for the winner.
